        <abstract> 
<p>Answers to CD’s questions on expressions among the Atnah and Espyox Indians of Nass River [see <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>, pp. 22, 232, 252, 260].</p> 
            <p>Discusses the debate in America over the relationship among Indian tribes. JTR does not believe Indians are all of one race; they are as varied as Europeans.</p>
            <p>[Forwarded to CD by Asa Gray.]</p>
        </abstract>
